Step 1: Repo Creation

https://github.com/mohansivaraman7/uptor_002_ai_ml_api
Pre-requisite: Ensure that you installed github in your laptop
    Link : https://git-scm.com/install/windows
    Instructions : Install with all default settings.

Step 2: Pushing my project into new branch in that Repo
   2.1 Enter into the Folder where you have your project
   2.2 After entering into initialize the git for communication
                 git init
   2.3 Add Files for the remote git
              git add .
   2.4 Commit the Files (saving to staging)
              git commit -m "my first project in git"
   2.5 Create Branch for the files to store
            git branch -M Master
   2.6 create a path to the origin
            git remote add origin https://github.com/mohansivaraman7/uptor_002_ai_ml_api.git
       2.6.1 It may ask you to add mail and username for firstname
             so add yourmail and yourusername
   2.7 git push -r origin Master
        2.7.1 set as upstream





